text: Arthur McBeath (17 June 1876 - 17 March 1945) was an Australian cricketer. He played twenty-eight first-class matches for New South Wales and South Australia between 1899/00 and 1907/08. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1876 births Category:1945 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:South Australia cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
